wikiText:
So called because the band thought the guitar riff sounded like something a cheesy hotel bar band might play.  The lyrics concern Cobain's ex Tobi Vail from [band]Bikini Kill[/band], with lines like &quot;I still smell her on you&quot;, making it a clear footnote to &quot;...Teen Spirit&quot;.

 Cobain later wrote an unsettling letter to Vail which read &quot;I don't write songs about you except Lounge Act, which I do not play except when my wife is not around.&quot;

